  "detailed_description": "MACHINE RUNAWAY is a third-person shooter game where you aim from 200 floors underground to the surface. The protagonist can transform into enemy characters. Make full use of the abilities of various enemy characters to advance the game to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/3e2c465ea36f0d909d56ead3a8db9bf3.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/3e2c465ea36f0d909d56ead3a8db9bf3.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/3e2c465ea36f0d909d56ead3a8db9bf3.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transform Into Enemies</h2><br>The protagonist can only shoot and kick, but can transform into enemy characters. Transforming allows you to use that character's attacks. Collect as many transformable characters as possible from treasure chests or by defeating bosses to gain an edge in battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/10b410ba77b59c70c823dea1d6625dc5.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/10b410ba77b59c70c823dea1d6625dc5.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/10b410ba77b59c70c823dea1d6625dc5.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Healing Items</h2><br>There are no healing items or skills. However, characters not in use gradually recover HP. Survive by strategically switching characters. Be cautious, as a character takes time to repair once destroyed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/12c07fc4ae65f85a95d77053b862308b.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/12c07fc4ae65f85a95d77053b862308b.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/12c07fc4ae65f85a95d77053b862308b.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>The protagonist, having developed 'transformation' technology, is deemed a dangerous robot with a bounty on their head. Hunted by other robots, he aims to escape to the surface from the bottommost level, 200 floors down. Fight off the attacking robots and aim for the surface.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/6fd29df8e6dbbc184850f7cc64b07100.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/6fd29df8e6dbbc184850f7cc64b07100.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/6fd29df8e6dbbc184850f7cc64b07100.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Localization</h2><br>Not fully localized. The subtitles that appear when you hover over the menu have been translated.",
  "about_the_game": "MACHINE RUNAWAY is a third-person shooter game where you aim from 200 floors underground to the surface. The protagonist can transform into enemy characters. Make full use of the abilities of various enemy characters to advance the game to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/3e2c465ea36f0d909d56ead3a8db9bf3.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/3e2c465ea36f0d909d56ead3a8db9bf3.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/3e2c465ea36f0d909d56ead3a8db9bf3.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transform Into Enemies</h2><br>The protagonist can only shoot and kick, but can transform into enemy characters. Transforming allows you to use that character's attacks. Collect as many transformable characters as possible from treasure chests or by defeating bosses to gain an edge in battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/10b410ba77b59c70c823dea1d6625dc5.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/10b410ba77b59c70c823dea1d6625dc5.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/10b410ba77b59c70c823dea1d6625dc5.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Healing Items</h2><br>There are no healing items or skills. However, characters not in use gradually recover HP. Survive by strategically switching characters. Be cautious, as a character takes time to repair once destroyed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/12c07fc4ae65f85a95d77053b862308b.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/12c07fc4ae65f85a95d77053b862308b.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/12c07fc4ae65f85a95d77053b862308b.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>The protagonist, having developed 'transformation' technology, is deemed a dangerous robot with a bounty on their head. Hunted by other robots, he aims to escape to the surface from the bottommost level, 200 floors down. Fight off the attacking robots and aim for the surface.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/6fd29df8e6dbbc184850f7cc64b07100.poster.avif?t=1709214958\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/6fd29df8e6dbbc184850f7cc64b07100.webm?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782650/extras/6fd29df8e6dbbc184850f7cc64b07100.mp4?t=1709214958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Localization</h2><br>Not fully localized. The subtitles that appear when you hover over the menu have been translated.",
